{"tid":2372393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國前公務員冒犯君主罪成囚43年半","createTime":"2021-01-19T15:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T05:11:42.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1975eb9cd2d2071e9852a25becfee3fa122c347b","tid":2372393,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:14:03.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】泰國一名前公務員因為轉發批評王室的錄音，被控冒犯君主罪，重判入獄43年半。<br />\n<br />\n65歲女被告到法院聽取裁決，她稱當年轉發錄音前思考不夠周詳，今次上了寶貴一課。她被控2014至2015年間在網上轉發錄音，批評君主制，29項罪名全部成立。<br />\n<br />\n今次是泰國歷來因為冒犯君主罪，而被判處的最重刑罰。人權組織透露，法庭原本裁定被告入獄87年，考慮到她認罪，將刑期減半。"},{"pid":"1e25e699de01adb123ba1f0c905de3db557a91b1","tid":2372393,"uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:14:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/44530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F44530&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmerktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=a4e418d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F44530&h=37407bd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/44530</a>"},{"pid":"463bcbd796ef04c77d17b42dfbf1cf7518fbca83","tid":2372393,"uid":148355,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:14:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家"},{"pid":"69437bbd5224f47911a3bf17199124db762e7a36","tid":2372393,"uid":174013,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:15:32.000Z","msg":"即係坐到死"},{"pid":"89a78bc5808991980ae612fe0c83b3f81e680fcf","tid":2372393,"uid":16344,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"真係痴撚線，不過而家世界就係咁㗎啦，我哋普通人邊度有得鬥"},{"pid":"4f83e3f57cf22355c13f874bc8129bcd864de799","tid":2372393,"uid":271516,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T15:17:07.000Z","msg":"同判死刑無分別<br />\n話說國王肺炎初期係咪消失左"},{"pid":"e7ec8295b4f821f7d15e48fa727a89db9433d919","